def calculate_max_earnings(blue_cards, red_cards):
    max_earnings = 1
    unique_blue_strings = set(blue_cards)
    for string in unique_blue_strings:
        earnings = blue_cards.count(string) - red_cards.count(string)
        max_earnings = max(max_earnings, earnings)
    return max_earnings
